4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with essential tech skills, particularly in JavaScript and Python. This 18-week program includes 16 weeks of coursework and 2 weeks for project presentation, featuring three classes per week with a low student-to-teacher ratio of 7:1. Participants will not require prior coding experience and can choose to learn in English or Spanish. The program culminates in a Full-Stack Developer certificate. Instructors Rodolfo Campos and Gabriel Salinas bring valuable industry experience to the course. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop